00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:19.260
Mwen aprann de tranbleman de tè an Ayiti a sou Skype

00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:22.260
Madanm mwen te voye yon mesaj pou mwen.

00:00:22.260 --> 00:00:24.260
“Woy, tranbleman tè"

00:00:24.260 --> 00:00:27.260
epi’l disparèt pou 25 minit

00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:31.260
Se te 25 minit nan panik absoli

00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:35.260
ke milyè de moun nan Etazini te santi

00:00:36.260 --> 00:00:39.260
M te pè de tsounami.

00:00:39.260 --> 00:00:41.260
S'am pa te reyalize

00:00:41.260 --> 00:00:44.260
se te gen yon pi gran panik an Ayiti

00:00:44.260 --> 00:00:47.260
epi kay yo t’ap kraze

00:00:47.260 --> 00:00:49.260
Nou tout wè foto

00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:52.260
kay kraze yo an Ayiti.

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:54.260
Sa yo se foto madanm mwen pran

00:00:54.260 --> 00:00:56.260
de twa jou apre tranbleman de tè a

00:00:56.260 --> 00:00:59.260
lè'm t’ap pase pa D.R. pou’m antre nan peyi a.

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:02.260
Sa se Palè Nasyonal la,

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:05.260
Ekivalan de palè blanch Ameriken an

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:08.260
Sa se pi gwo mache nan Karayib la

00:01:08.260 --> 00:01:11.260
gen anpil moun k’ap achte.

00:01:13.260 --> 00:01:15.260
Sa se yon kolèj pou enfimyè.

00:01:15.260 --> 00:01:18.260
Gen 300 enfimyè k’ap etidye.

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:21.260
general la ki bò kote’l la

00:01:21.260 --> 00:01:24.260
general la ki bò kote’l la.

00:01:24.260 --> 00:01:27.260
Sa se Ministè Ekonomi ak Finans la.

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:32.260
Nou tout tande

00:01:32.260 --> 00:01:35.260
anpil moun ki mouri

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:37.260
nan tranbleman tè an Ayiti a,

00:01:37.260 --> 00:01:40.260
men nou pa tande anpil

00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:43.260
de poukisa la vi moun sa yo te pèdi.

00:01:43.260 --> 00:01:45.260
Nou pa tande de

00:01:45.260 --> 00:01:48.260
poukisa kay yo kraze.

00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:50.260
Apre tout bagay, se te kay yo,

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:52.260
se pa te tranbleman tè a

00:01:52.260 --> 00:01:55.260
ki tiye 220,000 moun

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:58.260
blese 330,000,

00:01:58.260 --> 00:02:03.260
deplase 1.3 milyon moun

00:02:04.260 --> 00:02:06.260
ki koupe manje

00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:08.260
ak dlo ak provizyon

00:02:08.260 --> 00:02:11.260
pou tout on peyi

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:16.260
Sa se pi gran dezas nan zòn metwopoliten

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:19.260
nan deseni.

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:22.260
Epi li pa te yon dezas natirèl.

00:02:22.260 --> 00:02:25.260
Se te yon dezas de jeni.

00:02:25.260 --> 00:02:27.260
AIDG ap travay an Ayiti

00:02:27.260 --> 00:02:29.260
depi 2007,

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:31.260
bay sipò biznis ak jeni

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:33.260
pou ti biznis yo.

00:02:33.260 --> 00:02:37.260
Apre tranbleman tè ta, nou kòmanse vini ak enjenyè ki spesyalize nan tranbleman tè

00:02:37.260 --> 00:02:39.260
pou yo ka chèche konnen ki sa ki fè kay yo tonbe,

00:02:39.260 --> 00:02:42.260
pou yo ekzamine ki sa ki san danje, ki sa ki gen danje.

00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:45.260
Pandan n’ap travay ak MINUSTAH,

00:02:45.260 --> 00:02:47.260
ki se mission ONU in Ayiti,

00:02:47.260 --> 00:02:49.260
ansanm ak Ministè Travay Piblik,

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:51.260
avèk diferan NGO,

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:54.260
nou enspèkte 1500 kay.

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:57.260
Nou inspèkte lekòl

00:02:57.260 --> 00:02:59.260
ansanm ak kay prive.

00:02:59.260 --> 00:03:01.260
Nou inspèkte sant medical

00:03:01.260 --> 00:03:03.260
ak depo manje.

00:03:03.260 --> 00:03:05.260
Nou enspèkte ofis gouvènman yo.

00:03:05.260 --> 00:03:07.260
Sa se Ministè Jistis.

00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:09.260
Dèyè pòt sa

00:03:09.260 --> 00:03:12.260
se Achiv Jistis Nasyonal la.

00:03:12.260 --> 00:03:14.260
Kanmarad ki nan pòt la, Andre Filitrault,

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:16.260
se direktè

00:03:16.260 --> 00:03:20.260
Sant pou Rechèch Entèdisiplinè de Tranbleman de Tè

00:03:20.260 --> 00:03:23.260
nan Univèsite de Buffalo

00:03:23.260 --> 00:03:25.260
t’ap ekzamine’l pou’l wè si p’at gen danje

00:03:25.260 --> 00:03:27.260
pou ka sove achiv la.

00:03:27.260 --> 00:03:29.260
Andre di’m,

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:31.260
apre’l wè kay sa yo tonbe

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:34.260
menm jan chak fwa

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:37.260
pa gen nouvo rechèch.

00:03:37.260 --> 00:03:40.260
Pa gen anyen la nou pa konnen.

00:03:40.260 --> 00:03:43.260
Pwen echèk la toujou menm kote –

00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:46.260
mi ak beton yo pa mare byen nan kolòn yo--

00:03:46.260 --> 00:03:49.260
sa se yon twati siman ki pandye sou bò kay la –

00:03:51.260 --> 00:03:53.260
eskriti kite sipòte yon sèl kote,

00:03:53.260 --> 00:03:55.260
eskriti ki pa te simetrik,

00:03:55.260 --> 00:03:57.260
ki souke trè vyolan epi ki tonbe,

00:03:59.260 --> 00:04:01.260
move materyèl konstriksyon,

00:04:01.260 --> 00:04:03.260
pa ase siman,

00:04:03.260 --> 00:04:06.260
pa ase konpresyon nan blòk yo,

00:04:07.260 --> 00:04:09.260
fè reyanfòsman ki te two lis,

00:04:09.260 --> 00:04:12.260
fè reyanfòsman ki te ekspoze nan move tan epi ki rouye.

00:04:12.260 --> 00:04:15.260
Konnye a gen yon solisyon

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:17.260
pou tout pwoblèm say o.

00:04:17.260 --> 00:04:20.260
Epi nou konnen kòman pou nou bati byen.

00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:23.260
Prèv sa soti Chili,

00:04:23.260 --> 00:04:26.260
prèske yon mwa apre,

00:04:26.260 --> 00:04:29.260
lè tranbleman de tè de 8.8 mayitid a

00:04:30.260 --> 00:04:32.260
frape Chili.

00:04:32.260 --> 00:04:34.260
Sa se 500 fwa

00:04:34.260 --> 00:04:36.260
pi pisan ke 7.0

00:04:36.260 --> 00:04:39.260
ki frape Port-au-Prince

00:04:39.260 --> 00:04:41.260
500 fwa pi pisan,

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:44.260
epi sèl mwens ke mil mouri.

00:04:46.260 --> 00:04:48.260
Ajiste pou popilasyon dansite,

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:50.260
sa se mwens ke yon pousan

00:04:50.260 --> 00:04:53.260
enpak tranbleman tè Ayiti a.

00:04:54.260 --> 00:04:56.260
Se ki diferans

00:04:56.260 --> 00:04:59.260
antre Chili ak Ayiti?

00:04:59.260 --> 00:05:01.260
Estanda sismik

00:05:01.260 --> 00:05:04.260
ak masonnen fèmen,

00:05:04.260 --> 00:05:06.260
kote kay yo aji ansanm –

00:05:06.260 --> 00:05:08.260
mi ak kolòn,

00:05:08.260 --> 00:05:10.260
avèk twati ak beton

00:05:10.260 --> 00:05:13.260
mare ansanm pou yo ka sipòte yo chak,

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:17.260
autan ke yo kraze an moso manb epi tonbe.

00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:21.260
Si’w gade kay san an Chili,

00:05:21.260 --> 00:05:23.260
li rache an mwatwe,

00:05:23.260 --> 00:05:26.260
men li pa yon pil blòk kraze.

00:05:27.260 --> 00:05:29.260
Moun Chili yo t’ap bati ak masonnen fèmen

00:05:29.260 --> 00:05:31.260
pou deseni.

00:05:32.260 --> 00:05:36.260
Konnye a, AIDG ap travay ak KPFF Consulting Engineers,

00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:38.260
Architecture for Humanity,

00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:41.260
pou pote plis entrenman masonnen fèmen

00:05:41.260 --> 00:05:43.260
an Ayiti.

00:05:45.260 --> 00:05:47.260
Sa se Xantus Daniel.

00:05:47.260 --> 00:05:49.260
Li se yon mason,

00:05:49.260 --> 00:05:52.260
jusk yon travayè konstriksyon jeneral, li pa yon kontremèt,

00:05:52.260 --> 00:05:54.260
ki pran yonn nan entrenman nou yo.

00:05:54.260 --> 00:05:57.260
Nan travay pase li ya, li t’ap travay ansanm avèk boss li,

00:05:57.260 --> 00:06:00.260
epi yo t’ap kòmanse vide siman nan kolòn nan mal.

00:06:00.260 --> 00:06:02.260
Li pran boss li akote pou'l pale avèk li,

00:06:02.260 --> 00:06:05.260
epi li montre’l materyel masonnen fèmen yo.

00:06:05.260 --> 00:06:08.260
Li montre’l, “Ou konnen, nou pa bezwen fè sa mal.

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.260
Li p’ap koute nou pi chè

00:06:10.260 --> 00:06:13.260
pou nou fèl byen.”

00:06:13.260 --> 00:06:15.260
Epi yo refè kay la.

00:06:15.260 --> 00:06:17.260
Yo mare fè poto yo byen.

00:06:17.260 --> 00:06:19.260
Yo vide siman nan kolòn nan byen.

00:06:19.260 --> 00:06:21.260
Epi kay sa ap vinn san danje.

00:06:21.260 --> 00:06:23.260
Epi tout lòt kay

00:06:23.260 --> 00:06:25.260
yo bati aprè sa

00:06:25.260 --> 00:06:27.260
ap vinn san danje.

00:06:28.260 --> 00:06:30.260
Pou asire ke kay sa yo san danje,

00:06:30.260 --> 00:06:33.260
li pa’p pran lwa,

00:06:33.260 --> 00:06:35.260
l’ap pran chèche pale

00:06:35.260 --> 00:06:38.260
ak mason yo ki a tè a,

00:06:38.260 --> 00:06:41.260
epi ede yo aprann bon teknik.

00:06:43.260 --> 00:06:45.260
Konnye a gen anpil group k’ap fè sa.

00:06:45.260 --> 00:06:47.260
Kanmarad ki gen vès sou li a,

00:06:47.260 --> 00:06:49.260
Craig Toten,

00:06:49.260 --> 00:06:51.260
t’ap pouse devan

00:06:51.260 --> 00:06:54.260
mete dokiman deyò pou tout moun k’ap fè sa.

00:06:55.260 --> 00:06:57.260
Atravè Haiti Rewired,

00:06:57.260 --> 00:07:00.260
atravè Build Change, Architecture for Humanity,

00:07:00.260 --> 00:07:02.260
AIDG,

00:07:02.260 --> 00:07:04.260
gen yen posibilite

00:07:04.260 --> 00:07:07.260
pou chèch pale

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:10.260
ak 30000, 40000 mason

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:12.260
atravè peyi a

00:07:12.260 --> 00:07:15.260
epi kreye yon movman pou bati byen.

00:07:17.260 --> 00:07:19.260
Si’w lonje men’w ba moun yo ki sou tè a

00:07:19.260 --> 00:07:21.260
nan mwayen kolaboratif sa

00:07:21.260 --> 00:07:24.260
li ekstrèmman abòdab.

00:07:24.260 --> 00:07:28.260
Pou tout milya k’ap depanse nan rekonstwiksyon an,

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:30.260
ou ka antrene mason

00:07:30.260 --> 00:07:32.260
pou dola sou chak kay

00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:35.260
yo vinn bati pandan y’ap viv.

00:07:37.260 --> 00:07:39.260
Finalman, gen 2 mwayen

00:07:39.260 --> 00:07:41.260
ke ou ka rekonstwi Ayiti,

00:07:41.260 --> 00:07:43.260
mwayen ki kòmanse anwo a

00:07:43.260 --> 00:07:46.260
se mwayen sa Ayiti te konstwi pou deseni.

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:48.260
Mwayen sa a

00:07:48.260 --> 00:07:50.260
se yon kay ki konstwi mal

00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:52.260
ki pral kraze.

00:07:52.260 --> 00:07:55.260
Mwayen anba a se yon kay ki konstwi ak masonnen fèmen,

00:07:55.260 --> 00:07:57.260
kote mi yo mare ansanm,

00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:59.260
kay la an simetri,

00:07:59.260 --> 00:08:02.260
epi ka kanpe devan yon tranbleman tè.

00:08:02.260 --> 00:08:04.260
Pou tout dezas,

00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:07.260
gen yon opòtinite la

00:08:07.260 --> 00:08:09.260
pou konstwi bi bon kay

00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:11.260
pou lòt jenerasyon an,

00:08:11.260 --> 00:08:14.260
pou lè yon lòt tranbleman tè pase,

00:08:14.260 --> 00:08:16.260
li t’ap yon dezas

00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:18.260
otan ke yon trajedi.

00:08:19.260 --> 00:08:23.260
(Aplodisman)

